name: bothsid3s
description:
passive aggressiveness against both sides of all opinion
i always want more,
i always wanted more
i don't want one option, i want both, all of them
to then release them, set them free and let them fight each other
loving each other for being part of the same, hating each other for wanting to be the one who prevails
always fighting for more
more of the other
more of you
